      send_time: '2025-02-28T15:08:00'
    },
    {
      is_incoming: false,
      avatar: 'avatar-creator',
      content: '<p><strong>You:</strong> What is an AI agent, and how is it related to a digital persona?</p>',
      send_time: '2025-02-28T15:09:00'
    },
    {
      is_incoming: true,
      avatar: 'avatar-dp',
      content: '
        <p><strong>DP:</strong> An AI agent is a program or system designed to perform tasks autonomously, using artificial intelligence to process data, make decisions, and interact with users.</p>
        <p>In the context of a digital persona, an AI agent acts as a virtual representation of an individual, capable of mimicking their personality traits, knowledge, memories, and communication style. This allows it to engage in conversations across messengers and social media platforms, fully replicating the mannerisms and behavior of its &laquo;original&raquo; creator.</p>
      ',
      send_time: '2025-02-28T15:09:00'
    },
    {
      is_incoming: false,
      avatar: 'avatar-creator',
      content: '<p><strong>You:</strong> Can my Digital Person say something I wouldn&rsquo;t?</p>',
      send_time: '2025-02-28T15:12:00'
